  m_text: "Heads and Tails is a simple yet exciting casual game. The purpose is toflip
    the coin and try to guess which side will show face up.\n\nHow to Play:\n\n1.  
    Go to choose your bet value.\n2.  Make your choice: heads or tails?\n3.  Our
    \"gravity generators\" will start \n      flipping the coin.\n4.  If your guess
    was correct you win times 1.98 \n      the amount of your bet!."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
